snippet.title: Johnny Depp Loses The Sun Libel Case - Does This Mean Amber Heard Has Won? | Small Screen Stories
snippet.description:
Welcome back to Small Screen Stories. Today is a BIG show, and today we’ll be talking about: Johnny Depp losing his libel case, Sean Connery has passed away, Rosario Dawson has been confirmed as Ahsoka Tano in The Mandalorian, and we get into trouble over our exclusive article about the David Ayer Cut of Suicide Squad.

Don't forget to like and comment!
